CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 13, 1962, pg. 1, reads: "All-City Orchestra aspirants are shown during rehearsal last Saturday at Schenley High School. Left to right, front row: Michael Miladin, John Minadeo School; Bobby Hornickel, West Liberty; Robert Scherrer, West Liberty; Charles Hart, Madison, and Ralph Bucci, West Liberty. Back row: Nellie Sandridge, Banksville; Harold McCall, Fairywood; James Hein, Overbrook; Gordon Jacobs, Fairywood; Ricky Cantor, Colfax, and Barbara Beissinger, West Liberty. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: All-City Orchestra students, first row from left: Michael Miladin, Bobby Hornickel, Robert Scherrer, Charles Hart, Ralph Bucci; back row: Nellie Sandridge, Harold McCall, James Hein, Gordon Jacobs, Ricky Cantor, and Barbara Beissinger playing instruments in Schenley High School
